  <brief_title>The Impact of Weight Loss Induced by Bariatric Surgery or Nutritional Management on Sexual Function in Men With Severe Obesity</brief_title>
  <acronym>SexOb</acronym>
  <official_title>Comparing the Impact of Weight Loss Induced by Bariatric Surgery or Through a Standard Nutritional Management on Sexual Function and Sperm Quality in Men With Severe Obesity - Multicenter, Prospective</official_title>
